) when using work or an idea that isn=E2=80=99t your own.<br><br>

As a final step, you can use a free plagiarism detector or plagiarism remov=
er to check for copyright infringement. Grammarly=E2=80=99s online plagiari=
sm checker can help ensure you correctly identified and cited anything in y=
